The rapper has been teasing a new album for a while and has now revealed that the album will be titled Thuto and it s coming out on the 7th of May 2017. #THUTO 07/05/2017. Get ready tweeted Abuti FillUp, who also shared the album cover. If you recall correctly, the album cover was shot towards the end of 2016 by renowned New York photographer Jonathan Mannion. Jonathan has shot album covers for the likes of Nas and Jay Z. Until the album drops we ll keep listening to the music he s released so far. People would like to find out from you if you ll be getting yourself a copy of Thuto when it drops. Brought to you by People Magazine For more news your way, follow The Citizen on Facebook and Twitter.